    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      MazeTutorial()
      Creates a specific maze game designed to teach the user how to play In addition to everything a Maze Game keeps track of, a MazeTutorial keeps track of what tip it is currently on, how long the tip has been displayed and whether the tip is visible or not
